{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idd39983bb-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s781"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"781"},"text":"§ 781.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this subchapter, the following definitions shall apply:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd39983bc-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s781/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Board","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The term “Board” means the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd39983bd-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s781/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Depository institution","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The term “depository institution” has the same meaning as in section 3 of the Federal Deposit Insurance Act.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd39983be-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370","identifier":"/us/usc/t11/s781/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Clearing bank","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The term “clearing bank” means an uninsured State member bank, or a corporation organized under section 25A of the Federal Reserve Act, which operates, or operates as, a multilateral clearing organization pursuant to section 409 ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002035"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002035"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation Improvement Act of 1991."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idd39983bf-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/554/s1/a/5/tI/s112/c/5/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–554, § 1(a)(5) [title I, § 112(c)(5)(B)]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-12-21"},"text":"Dec. 21, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/2763"},"text":"114 Stat. 2763","children":[],"tail":", 2763A–394.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idd39983c0-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idd39983c1-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idd39983c2-3a6f-11f1-8dc6-9561437cf370"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 3 of the Federal Deposit Insurance Act, referred to in par. (2), is classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1813"},"text":"section 1813 of Title 12","children":[],"tail":", Banks and Banking."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 25A of the Federal Reserve Act, referred to in par. (3), popularly known as the Edge Act, is classified to subchapter II (§ 611 et seq.) of chapter 6 of Title 12, Banks and Banking. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s611"},"text":"section 611 of Title 12","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 409 of the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation Improvement Act of 1991, referred to in par. (3), which was classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s4422"},"text":"section 4422 of Title 12","children":[],"tail":", Banks and Banking, was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/tVII/s740"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, title VII, § 740","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-07-21"},"text":"July 21, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/1729"},"text":"124 Stat. 1729","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
